{"title":"巨轮——松山芭蕾舞团《祇园祭》观后","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——松山芭蕾舞团《祇园祭》观后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑风在后退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶云在溃败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捕快狼狈滚下台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们妄想压制人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎挡得住巨轮滚滚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，“贱民”和农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臂相挽，肩相并，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"协力同心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着历史的彩车前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时，轮子隐到了幕后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时，轮子被砸坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时，仿佛天昏地又黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民好象被包围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兔子的尾巴，长不了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民对反动派扬声大笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔出敌人射来的箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺向敌人的胸口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江东去曲折流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不回头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想喝住历史的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就一定被它踢开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想损害人民的彩车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就一定被它辗得粉碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑风在后退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶云在溃败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捕快狼狈滚下台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩绳长，意气扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花笠在旋舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鹤在飞翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨轮滚滚，歌声嘹亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民紧握历史的缰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万山千关都能闯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月十六日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}